00:04:30.990 --> 00:04:37.039
1. Writing and reading are things that not
everyone can do. So they create a class distinction,

00:04:37.039 --> 00:04:41.240
one that in fact survives to this day. Foraging
social orders were relatively egalitarian;

00:04:41.240 --> 00:04:45.729
but the Mesopotamians had slaves and they
played this metaphorically resonant sport

00:04:45.729 --> 00:04:51.050
that was like polo except instead of riding
on horses you rode on other people.

00:04:51.050 --> 00:04:54.510
And written language played an important role
in widening the gap between classes.

00:04:54.510 --> 00:05:00.520
2. Once writing enters the picture, you have actual
history instead of just a lot of guesswork &amp; archaeology.

00:05:00.520 --> 00:05:05.150
3. Without writing, I would not have a job,
so I'd like to personally thank Mesopotamia

00:05:05.150 --> 00:05:09.509
